"{\"uid\": \"pakobserver.net-caelab-books-50m-free-olympic-title-defence\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Caeleb Dressel shook off his doubts and booked a chance to defend his 50m freestyle Olympic title in Paris with a victory on Friday at the US Olympic swimming trials.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}, {\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999952601684, \"rank\": 4.739927654827072e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 141, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"score\": 0.5975359342915416, \"rank\": 0.6735395189003551, \"text\": \"US Olympic swimming trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel, whose five gold medals at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021 included the 50m and 100m free and 100m fly, booked his first individual swim in Paris after missing out with a third-place finish in the 100m free.\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999952601684, \"rank\": 4.739927654827072e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory capped a long, often rocky road back to the top for the seven-time Olympic gold medallist, who stepped away from the sport abruptly in 2022.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel looked in vintage form at Lucas Oil Stadium, home of the NFL's Indianapolis Colts, exploding off the blocks to win the 50 free in 21.41sec.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.8828655484396805, \"rank\": 0.13105976474899378, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Colts\", \"score\": 0.9996003376005942, \"rank\": 0.0002924605928066586, \"text\": \"Indianapolis Colts\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Colts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_Colts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The time makes him the fourth-fastest in the world this year, a list led by Australian Cameron McEvoy.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.5987998097740536, \"rank\": 0.6674318208343982, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cameron McEvoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew it was one of my toughest nights,\\\" said Dressel, who would return to top the times in the 100m butterfly semi-finals in 50.79sec.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(I was) not feeling great or anything special, so I just had to gut it out tonight.\\\"\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With his wife, Meghan, celebrating in the stands with their four-month-old son, August, in her arms, Dressel checked the 50m free scoreboard and gave a mighty fist pump before acknowledging the crowd.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris Guiliano, winner of the 100m free and runner-up in the 200m free this week, was second in 21.69 - with Matt King shut out of the Olympic berths by an agonizing one-hundredth of a second as he finished third in 21.70.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel, 27, said his relaxed demeanor on deck in Indianapolis has belied some tense moments behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.8771237964703502, \"rank\": 0.09040614412526055, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is parts of this meet, I have had some very low lows,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is parts in my hotel room that are not on camera, talking with my wife, talking with my therapist - it has not been smooth sailing this whole meet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, he added, he's trying to relish the good times after his extended break that refreshed his relationship to the sport.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That includes the warmth he's felt from the crowd, which has topped 20,000 at the finals ses-sions.-AFP    \\u00a9All rights reserved | Pakistan Observer\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": []}]}"